title: Loki's Incredibly Busy Day
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2y12nd4

by Arvari

Loki is dead. He died a good, heroic death. He is sure he deserved his place in Valhalla. So it’s pretty disappointing when he finds himself in Hel, being greeted by the sister he never wanted to see again.

A sister with a deal he just cannot refuse. Being brought back to life in exchange for saving the whole universe and making Hel a little bit less crowded? Oh, yes, please. All he needs to do is to be a good guy and everything will be fine.

But being a good guy is so tiresome and Loki is, above all, a God of Mischief…

summary:
Unpopular Opinion 
I feel Black Cat could easily get a series or solo film about her .. Easy in terms of plot 
For the plot you...
body:
Unpopular Opinion

I feel Black Cat could easily get a series or solo film about her .. Easy in terms of plot

For the plot you could talk about

  1. Young Felicia Hardy in her school days when her father Walter Hardy was a cat burglar himself
  2. Talk about her traumatic experience in College that caused her to drop out
  3. Her then becoming a Cat burglar herself
  4. Meeting peter

Etc etc..

Obviously it probably won’t even be in that order but it’s just the little things.

(Please be sure to share and comment , i love talking about this stuff.)

hey guys!! it’s me, karina, if you remember (yikes!!) 
i know ive been inactive for a while, but that’s because i was working...
body:
hey guys!! it’s me, karina, if you remember (yikes!!)

i know ive been inactive for a while, but that’s because i was working full time in the summer and now im back at university (which is no excuse, im just a shit human sometimes)

i want to get back into writing and i am going to start being a lot more active again!!! bear with me as i get back into the swing of things, but i want to thank everyone who stayed with me during my hiatus — i love you all 💛💛💛
